data.description: Great Opportunity to own this 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath Pool home. Updated and remodeled. Move In Ready! Great Room Floor Plan with Newer Neutral Ceramic Tile throughout (No Carpet). Kitchen with Newer Wood Cabinets, Beautiful Back Splash, Newer Stainless Steel Appliances, Breakfast Nook with Slider leading to Lanai. Bathrooms Updated with tile, Newer Wood Cabinets, New Fixtures. 3 Bedrooms with Freshly Polished Terrazzo Flooring. Crown Molding, All New Interior Doors, Light Fixtures and Ceiling Fans. Enjoy the Private (Fenced) backyard with Sparkling Large Pool, Covered area- Great for BBQing. Newer Washer and Dryer. Roof and A/C Replaced. Great Location-Pinellas Trail, Shopping, County Parks, Clearwater Mall Nearby.
